(44, 17, 27, 19, 19, 1, 6, 'seek the Lord', 'Seeking God in Creation', 'Both passages emphasize the pursuit of God through creation. Acts 17:27 speaks of seeking the Lord, while Psalms 19:1-6 illustrates how the heavens declare His glory, inviting people to recognize His presence.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 17, 27, 44, 15, 17, 17, 'seek the Lord', 'Seeking the Lord', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of seeking the Lord. Acts 17:27 speaks of seeking God, while Acts 15:17 mentions that men might seek after the Lord, highlighting a shared focus on the pursuit of divine connection.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
