(44, 18, 1, 44, 19, 1, 1, 'Paul departed from Athens, and came to Corinth', 'Paul''s Journey to Ephesus', 'This connection highlights Paul''s movement between cities, first arriving in Corinth and later traveling to Ephesus. Both passages emphasize the continuity of Paul''s missionary work as he moves from one significant location to another.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 18, 1, 47, 1, 1, 1, 'Paul departed from Athens, and came to Corinth', 'Paul''s Mission to Corinth', 'This connection highlights Paul''s journey to Corinth, where he later addresses the church in his letter. Both passages emphasize Paul''s role in establishing and nurturing the Christian community in Corinth.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
