(44, 18, 2, 46, 16, 19, 19, NULL, 'Connection of Aquila and Priscilla', 'This connection highlights the presence of Aquila and Priscilla in both passages. They are mentioned in Acts as having come from Rome and later greet the church in 1 Corinthians, indicating their ongoing role in the early Christian community.', 'theme', 0.363, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
