(44, 18, 4, 42, 4, 16, 16, 'every sabbath', 'Sabbath Synagogue Practices', 'Both passages emphasize the practice of attending the synagogue on the Sabbath. Acts 18:4 describes reasoning in the synagogue every Sabbath, while Luke 4:16 highlights Jesus'' custom of going into the synagogue on that day.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
